		in math blogging platforms. Use $latex your latex code here$ or [latex]your latex code here[/latex]
		to include in your posts and comments. Enjoy all sorts of options and embrace your inner nerd.'=>'LaTeX は、複雑な方程式や数式を入力するのに適したパワフルなマークアップ言語です。
